{"tid":1947323,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU側拍私照遭外流！U領低胸「側身露半球」","createTime":"2020-03-28T08:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T17:02:09.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ddbceed483e4d870612ab68dce92b8f06c202631","tid":1947323,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:13:05.000Z","msg":"南韓26歲人氣女星IU(李知恩)，日前登上雜誌封面《W KOREA》引起網友熱烈討論，這兩日網路上又流出當初拍攝時工作人員所錄製的側拍影片，意外秀出IU凹凸有致的好身材，再次引發話題。<br />\n<br />\n才剛結束居家隔離便投入工作的IU，這兩日陸續公開她所拍攝的雜誌內頁美照展現迷人魅力，只見她換上多套造型，時而甜美時而帥氣讓網友們相當驚艷。<br />\n<br />\n其中一套酒紅色深V上衣搭配高衩黑裙，以及銀色亮片深U洋裝最受到大家注意，在網路上流出的工作人員側拍照及影片中，可以看到IU隨著攝影師指示擺動，側身時隱約露出黑影深溝與性感北半球，讓網友們忍不住暴動，大讚「IU身材太好了」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/fashion/20200328001054-263903?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Ffashion%2F20200328001054-263903%3Fchdtv&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=097a6a92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/fashion/20200328001054-263903?chdtv</a>"},{"pid":"ec94dc46a5cc8411334e768bff02a8cdc3f10c77","tid":1947323,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2020-03-24/900/20200324003754.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2020-03-24%2F900%2F20200324003754.jpg&h=69d019a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暴動了"},{"pid":"53c295955c70fe4bb32c7e90cb4144a8b966f826","tid":1947323,"uid":231640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5af2337ef3eff35ea4e2b40c610a3fb12daed66","tid":1947323,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:21:06.000Z","msg":"IU咩cup? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc97ddffc3b1e688ec6213d6dc7d47d9